    {
      "title": "埃鲁德·基普乔格",
      "link": "https://baike.baidu.com/item/埃鲁德·基普乔格/9234190",
      "snippet": "\"埃鲁德·基普乔格(Eliud Kipchoge),1984年11月5日出生于肯尼亚南迪郡卡普西西瓦,是肯尼亚男子马拉松运动员｡ 2003年,基普乔格获得世界田径锦标赛男子5000米冠军｡2004年,他获得雅典奥运会男子5000米铜牌｡2008年,他摘得2008年北京奥运会男子5000米银牌｡2013年4月,基普乔格首次出战全程马拉松,以2小时05分30秒的成绩获得汉堡马拉松冠军并刷新赛道纪录｡",
      "date": "2025-03-20 17:11:57"
    },
    {
      "title": "Kenya's Eliud Kipchoge sets new world record at Berlin Marathon 2022 - Chinadaily.com.cn",
      "link": "https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202209/25/WS633024e1a310fd2b29e79971.html",
      "snippet": "Kenya's Eliud Kipchoge celebrates as he wins the Berlin Marathon and breaks the World Record in Berlin, Germany, Sept 25, 2022. [Photo/Agencies] BERLIN - Eliud Kipchoge from Kenya set a new world record of two hours, one minute and nine seconds to claim the 48th Berlin Marathon title here on Sunday. The 37-year-old Kenyan staged a dominant performance and bettered his own record from 2018 by 30 seconds with a wire-to-wire victory. Kipchoge and his pacemakers immediately took the lead after the start. Only Ethiopia's Andamlak Belihu and fellow countryman Guye Adola were able to keep up with Kipchoge, as the trio beat the previous world record ",
      "date": "2022-09-25 17:52:00"
